Daniel Keith Swain (amụrụ n'August 18, 1983), nke a maara dị ka Danny!, bụ onye America na-agụ egwu, ónyé na-eti egwu, onye mmepụta na ónyé na-ede egwu.

Swain ghọrọ onye a ma ama mgbe ọ rụchara ọrụ mbụ ya na Late Night na Jimmy Fallon, ebe ọ malitere egwu ya "Evil". Mgbè ọ sonyeere Okayplayer Records, Danny! wepụtara abọm ya Payback, nke AllMusic kwùrù dị ka otu n'ime mbipụta hip-hop kachasị mma n'afọ. N'afọ 2013, magazin Ebony depụtara Swain n'etiti ndị ọzọ na-eto eto na-ese ihe na "Ndị ndu nke ụlọ akwụkwọ ọhụrụ", na-akpọ Swain otu n'ime mmadụ ole na ole "ndị na-emepụta ihe".

Swain edeela egwu ndabere nke etinyela n'ọtụtụ ihe nkírí na mmemme telivishọn, ọkachasị usoro ihe nkiri FOX bụ Bob's Burgers nke e nyèrè Swain ihe nrite Emmy maka onyinye ya na ihe omume nke meriri na ngalaba mmemme animated pụtara ìhè na 69th Primetime Emmy Awards na 2017.

A mụrụ Swain, naanị nwa nke nné na nnà ndị agha, na Killeen, Texas wee kwaga Columbia, South Carolina, mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na ụma. Ọ gara Richland Northeast High School wee malite ịchụso egwu dị ka ihe ntụrụndụ n'afọ nke abụọ ya. Swain malitere ide okwu nke ya ma dekọọ egwu dị ka ihe ngosi màkà mmepụta ya.
